  <span id="freeText3693279656606189217" style="display:none">PAIN<br />SO, SO MUCH PAIN<br />I FORGOT HOW AGONIZING THAT ENDING WAS<br />AHHHHHHHHHHH<br /><br />review to come when I stop dying<br /><br /><br />___<br /><br />REREADING BECAUSE I LOVE TO SUFFER 🤪✌️<br />IT'S TIME TO RIP OPEN MY SCARS AGAIN 🤡✋<br />THIS BOOK HAS MADE ME CRY SO MANY TIMES YOU DON'T EVEN UNDERSTAND- 😃👍<br /><br />buddy reread with a bunch of amazing humans. we are ready to cry<br /><br /><br /><br />_____<br /><br /><br />I. AM. WRECKED.<br /><br />My heart has been torn out of my chest, stepped on, rolled in the dirt, and smashed into a million shards with the hammer of heartbreak. It's been ripped into shreds, thrown into the fire, and burned. I can't anymore. I just can't. Someone dig me a grave. <br /><br />Sarah J. Maas, I hate you. But I love you. But I hate you.</span>
