        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1730710276" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15216341103758572573">*.) <a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ibg8gGc9yjg' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Assassin&apos;s Blade</a> ★★★★★<br/>1.) <a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2unlZ5BnyrA' rel='nofollow noopener'>Throne of Glass</a> ★★★★★<br/>2.) <a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RxtFXrG-9L4&amp;list=PLhD0V9FzRQG_N7FuK6GkE0ljzHB2onBz0&amp;t' rel='nofollow noopener'>Crown of Midnight</a> ★★★★★<br/>3.) <a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gSjyXiXYdSk&amp;list=PLhD0V9FzRQG_N7FuK6GkE0ljzHB2onBz0&amp;index=4' rel='nofollow noopener'>Heir of Fire</a> ★★★★★<br/>4.) <a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J_YU8zH6Y3A&amp;list=PLhD0V9FzRQG_N7FuK6GkE0ljzHB2onBz0&amp;index=5' rel='nofollow noopener'>Queen of Shadows</a> ★★★★★<br/>5.) <a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ysdOM1XyINs&amp;t=' rel='nofollow noopener'>Empire of Storms</a> ★★★★★<br/>6.) <a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D3n9eyVGAJw&amp;t=' rel='nofollow noopener'>Tower of Dawn</a> ★★★★★<br/>7.) <a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CDzUuxIzlsE' rel='nofollow noopener'>Kingdom of Ash</a> ★★★★★<br/><br/>-----------------------------------------------<br/><br/>First read May 2015<br/>Reread August 2016<br/>Reread October 2018<br/><br/>Still hurts.<br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText15216341103758572573" style="display:none">*.) <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ibg8gGc9yjg" rel="nofollow noopener">The Assassin's Blade</a> ★★★★★<br />1.) <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2unlZ5BnyrA" rel="nofollow noopener">Throne of Glass</a> ★★★★★<br />2.) <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RxtFXrG-9L4&amp;list=PLhD0V9FzRQG_N7FuK6GkE0ljzHB2onBz0&amp;t" rel="nofollow noopener">Crown of Midnight</a> ★★★★★<br />3.) <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gSjyXiXYdSk&amp;list=PLhD0V9FzRQG_N7FuK6GkE0ljzHB2onBz0&amp;index=4" rel="nofollow noopener">Heir of Fire</a> ★★★★★<br />4.) <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J_YU8zH6Y3A&amp;list=PLhD0V9FzRQG_N7FuK6GkE0ljzHB2onBz0&amp;index=5" rel="nofollow noopener">Queen of Shadows</a> ★★★★★<br />5.) <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ysdOM1XyINs&amp;t=" rel="nofollow noopener">Empire of Storms</a> ★★★★★<br />6.) <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D3n9eyVGAJw&amp;t=" rel="nofollow noopener">Tower of Dawn</a> ★★★★★<br />7.) <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CDzUuxIzlsE" rel="nofollow noopener">Kingdom of Ash</a> ★★★★★<br /><br />-----------------------------------------------<br /><br />First read May 2015<br />Reread August 2016<br />Reread October 2018<br /><br />Still hurts.<br /><br /></span>
