rt: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</a><br><br>✦ <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3677961885?book_show_action=false&amp;from_review_page=1" rel="nofollow noopener">The Assassin and the Underworld: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</a><br><br>✦ <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3679098696?book_show_action=false&amp;from_review_page=1" rel="nofollow noopener">The Assassin and the Empire: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</a></b><br><br><b>SAMLAENA</b> IS THE ONE TRUE PAIR AND NOBODY CAN CHANGE MY MIND.<br><br>THANK YOU <b>SARAH</b> FOR BREAKING MY PATHETIC MORTAL SOUL.<br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1607314206i/30484665._SY540_.png" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>Now excuse me while I listen to this <b>
